Package javabank

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Account
    The Account class handles the id number, balance and customer and account type.
    AccountIDGenerator
    The AccountIDGenerator class handles the account id number generation(incrementation).
    ApplicationClose
    The ApplicationClose class provides the close action for the Teller application.
    ChequeAccount
    The ChequeAccount class handles the issuing of cheques.
    DepositAccount
    The DepositAccount class handles depositing and withdrawal of money.
    NewAccountDialog
    The NewAccountDialog class handles creation of a new account via a dialog window.
    SetFocusWindowAdapter
    The SetFocusWindowAdapter Class Provides the set focus action for the Teller application.
    StudentAccount
    The StudentAccount class specifically handles Overdraft limits for students.
    Teller
    This is the main Application and demonstrates the Teller class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AccountType
    The AccountType enumerator gives a list of labelled constants to identify the account type (I just placed this in to get the hang of using enums).
